<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٦٠٧ - حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5898">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ الْمُثَنَّى </a>قَالَ حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى بْنُ سَعِيدٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/644">إِسْمَاعِيلَ </a>حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5235">قَيْسٌ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1339">حُذَيْفَةَ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ <span class="c2">«تَعَلَّمَ أَصْحَابِي الْخَيْرَ وَتَعَلَّمْتُ الشَّرَّ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>